## REST
- [API-REST-01] **MUST** use plural nouns for resources; POST/GET/PATCH/DELETE.
- [API-REST-02] **MUST** return `201 + Location` on create; `202` for async; `409` on conflict; `422` on validation.
- [API-REST-03] **SHOULD** standardize pagination/filtering/sorting; document query params.

## GraphQL
- [API-GQL-01] **MUST** keep queries read-only; mutations for changes; subscriptions for events.
- [API-GQL-02] **SHOULD** provide examples to avoid under/over-fetching.

## gRPC
- [API-GRPC-01] **MUST** evolve proto schemas backward-compatibly; use rich error details.
- [API-GRPC-02] **MAY** use streaming when it materially improves UX/efficiency.

## Versioning
- [API-V-01] **MUST** apply semantic versions to APIs/schemas; announce deprecations with timeline & migration guide.
